summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 5576 for the improving the Alley between Blocks 11 and 12, Front Street Cable Addition, and between Blocks 11 and 12, Supplemental Plat to the Front Street Cable Addition, being the alley between 1st Avenue West and Queen Anne Avenue, from West McGraw Street to West Smith Street; by paving and otherwise improving the same, under Ordinance No. 73080, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
